% Junyi Sun, sunjunyi, 1001350183
 
S -> NP VP

% Basic noun phrases
NP -> N | NPROSUB | NPROOBJ | NPROPER | NPOSSESS  
NP -> DET N
NP -> DET ADJP N
NP -> DET N PP
NP -> ADJPOSSESS N

% Basic verb phrases
VP -> V S 
VP -> V NP
VP -> VP PP
VP -> VP NP PP

% Auxiliary System 
VP -> VPSIMP | VPPERF | VPPROGRS | VPPROGPERF | VPPASSIVE
VPSIMP -> VPAST | V | V3S | MODAL V
VPPERF -> AUXHAVE VPASTPA | MODAL AUXHAVE VPASTPA
VPPROGRS -> AUXBE VING | MODAL AUXBE VING
VPPROGPERF -> AUXHAVE AUXBE VING | MODAL AUXHAVE AUXBE VING
VPPASSIVE -> AUXBE VPASTPA | AUXHAVE AUXBE VPASTPA | MODAL AUXHAVE AUXBE VPASTPA

% Sub-categorization for only past tense
VPAST -> VPAST_NO | VPAST_NP NP | VPAST_NPVP NP VP | VPAST_NPNP NP NP | VPAST_NPPP NP PP | VPAST_TOV PTO | VPAST_PPPP PP PP | VPAST_PP PP | VPAST_PP ADVP | VPAST_S CON S | VPAST_NPS NP CON S

% Other phrases
PP -> P NP | P VP
PTO -> P V | P V NP 

ADJP -> ADJ | ADJ ADJP 
ADVP -> ADV PP | ADV VP | VP ADV 
